Description:
	Save Gnome Files (Nautilus) file manager window locations and folders.
	
Usage:
    Install wmctrl package
    Install python-nautilus package
    python2 setup.py
    
Manual install:
    Place this script in the users home ~/.local/share/nautilus-python/extensions/
    chmod u+x ~/.local/share/nautilus-python/extensions/window-monitor.py
    Place the other 2 scripts in user home ~/.local/share/nautilus-python/
    chmod u+x ~/.local/share/nautilus-python/window-monitor-*.py
    Run the Startup Applications program
        Click Add button
        Name: 'Folder Save'
        Command: browse to home ~/.local/share/nautilus-python/ and select window-monitor-login.py
        Click Add button
